#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
24HG Forge Smart Game Launch — Intelligent per-game optimization daemon

Automatically detects game launches and applies optimal settings per-game.
Makes 24HG Forge feel like a premium gaming OS with zero user configuration.

Commands:
    daemon              Run background monitoring daemon
    apply [appid]       Manually apply optimizations for a game
    config [appid]      View/edit per-game configuration
    status              Show current optimization state
    rules               List all built-in game rules
    log                 Show recent launch history

Part of 24HG Forge — The 24 Hour Gaming Operating System
https://24hgaming.com
"""

